node.text: JH Town weekend concert was one for the books see y’all next year! s/o @spotify @wescoremore @rapcaviar

node.text: Women’s Empowerment Bruch was amazing, can’t thank these amazing entrepreneurs enough for taking time out their schedule to participate in my weekend JH-Town 🖤
